########
By Nytimz

Renames The Deputy relic to the Commando Peacekeeper relic and: 
1) Increases Shotgun Fire rate upto +80% (-44% decrease in fire interval)
2) Increases Shotgun Damage upto +45%
3) Increases Shotgun Reload Speed upto +48%
4) Increases Shotgun Accuracy upto +100% (-50% decrease in weapon spread)
5) Regenerates Shotgun Ammo

Similar to equipping a Commando COM with Scattershot skill in BL1 but in Relic form and with additional Bonuses to Accuracy and Reload Speed.
Why did I choose The Deputy Badge relic to mod? It was one of the few with more than one Effect slot (has 5) and is a quest reward.

########

set GD_Artifacts.A_Item_Unique.Artifact_Deputy ItemName Commando Peacekeeper

